Welcome to the Wiki! Anyone can edit the wiki, and if you have any trouble its easy to find wiki:wikispot:Help with Editing help. Anyone can contribute, change, and add; however we do discourage removing information. Most websites you go to are static  you only read them. This is a very different place.

What we are Mission Statement aiming for is a place to record Davis culture, Spots And Places places, spots  everything!  This is an experiment in community and a project that can be fruitful for Town History years to come to both old and new in Davis.

Everyone these days has their own personal Blogs blog. They write down everyday activities, things they do, places they go. But how about the City of Davis city itself? Imagine this as sort of a blog for Davis itself. A place for sharing, listening, learning, growing and exploring. This is also a place to learn about collaborative editing; the pages here are generally not the reflection of a single person, but the work of many editors over time.

So, go Photo Requests grab your camera and Navigating Davis explore Davis!  Reviews Write a review of your favorite place. Share your favorite thing to do on Regular Events Tuesdays, or a Photo Requests picture of your favorite Downtown downtown establishment.  There are literally thousands of topics to explore, and theres room to add your own perspective at every turn.

The wikis content, its meaning, its purposeits up to you.  As a general rule you should contribute content you think will be helpful or insightful to others, but even this rule can be broken at times. Interesting things stay; bad content gets cleaned up, expanded upon, improved, or removed. Never be afraid to try something new, to edit something, to make your voice heard.

This is our place, our resource, our voice.

If youre ready to get started, check out the Davis Wiki Guide.

Live in the surrounding area?  You might like to visit and participate in the wiki:sacramento:Front Page Sacramento Wiki, wiki:woodland:Front Page Woodland Wiki, wiki:westsac:Front Page West Sacramento Wiki, wiki:vacaville:Front Page Vacaville Wiki, or other Nearby Wikis Nearby City Wikis.
